name: Pluto Message
description:
Pluto was our meeting point, that's what they told me in a "dream", then the question arose, why was declassified as a planet?

One day I descended to hades with my friends from that dimension, in the end I talked with Pluto, he gave me a dagger stating that with it I would achieve any wish, but that many had gone mad on the way and now they were living like zombies.

Some time later an amulet came to me in the material world, I realized that it had the symbol of the bident on it, a two-pointed scepter, the weapon of Pluto.

Now I am ready, I'll see you there.

Gal Groisman | Montevideo | 2019
